Violations of this license by third parties.

Any other damages resulting from the use of the Software.


4. Violation Notice

4.1. In the event of a violation of this license, you are required to cease using the Software and delete all copies from your devices.

4.2. The author reserves the right to terminate access to the Software or its updates for users who violate the terms of this license.

